\# BGI – Blockchain Gemological Institute  
  
\> A blockchain-based NFT protocol for diamond grading and certification    
\> Official Website: \[bgi.xyz\](https://bgi.xyz)  
  
BGI (Blockchain Gemological Institute) is the world’s first digital certification authority that combines the \*\*diamond 6C standard\*\* with \*\*non-fungible tokens (NFTs)\*\*. By leveraging blockchain’s immutability and transparency, we generate a unique digital certificate for each diamond, fundamentally solving industry pain points such as certificate forgery, inconsistent grading standards, and missing provenance records.  
  
